OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy with
OL,6,Fspells of showery rain, and murky
OL,7,Fconditions developing in the
OL,8,Fsouthwest. Rain will be locally heavy
OL,9,Fat times in the evening before
OL,10,Fbecoming briefly drier for a time.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FA partly cloudy day with
OL,13,Fshowers or longer spells of rain,
OL,14,Foften rather heavy with a risk of
OL,15,Fthunder.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,18,FUnsettled and rather changeable
OL,19,Fthrough this period with showers or
OL,20,Flonger spells of rain. Often rather
OL,21,Fbreezy.
